Backend locally:

cd backend
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000


Frontend locally:

cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
open http://localhost:5173 (set VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000 in .env if needed)


With Docker:

docker compose up --build